績也可以司法覆核，以非法考試為由要求撤銷。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88fa751bea5b809f406419ba10e1e08621324cae","tid":1949310,"uid":123192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e47bb36b42883111a2e6c1b0f7bb66946fc66f5","tid":1949310,"uid":112622,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:32:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:39:19.000Z","msg":"醫學生要中下肺炎 增加自己抗體 咁第日就唔怕入dirty team<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74826f3a035f4334f8bff188571bde5f834fe778","tid":1949310,"uid":196975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88fa751bea5b809f406419ba10e1e08621324cae","tid":1949310,"uid":123192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e47bb36b42883111a2e6c1b0f7bb66946fc66f5","tid":1949310,"uid":112622,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:32:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:39:19.000Z","msg":"醫學生要中下肺炎 增加自己抗體 咁第日就唔怕入dirty team<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:41:09.000Z","msg":"已經有同學疑似中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;大家今個禮拜考完ENT有冇人覺得有啲唔舒服...明明成個月冇出過街...只係返去PWH考左兩次written...EOM個陣記得有人係咁咳...諗住final mb postpone...但係依家又照樣考...真心想知道有冇其他同學仔近日都有唔舒服？不如一齊去A&amp;E驗... 如果我中左一定係考試到惹到...個人熱熱地但係度又冇燒...好驚中招, 唔想defer啊... 如果真係有同學屋企人中招就可以解釋到 (#CU1047A) 不如全部人考之前做一次快速測試...雖然冇嘢可以阻到faculty考試... btw希望大家都冇事 溫書加油 唔好死&quot;"},{"pid":"0d683c8ca33ada899f13aa13f4dd6f9b218cfbf7","tid":1949310,"uid":57397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:58:06.000Z","msg":"班教授唔是叫人唔好出街咩<br />\n身體卻很誠實<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bb6caf1db33ccc7578b91e4f4629686e4a95f9c","tid":1949310,"uid":196975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df9284f0cfa05c54eac5be8f4558d9bae7a16300","tid":1949310,"uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:36:01.000Z","msg":"睇唔到醫學院個考試有乜咁特別，可以得到豁免"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T15:20:28.000Z","msg":"好似話啱啱批左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d924e396164809272f33e7b8844d4a9a6d103b9","tid":1949310,"uid":123696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbffcb6db22c2b428ba623e5f64c5e2b486a06cd","tid":1949310,"uid":196975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df9284f0cfa05c54eac5be8f4558d9bae7a16300","tid":1949310,"uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:36:01.000Z","msg":"睇唔到醫學院個考試有乜咁特別，可以得到豁免"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:37:35.000Z","msg":"理論上考試係計教育用途。如果醫學院堅持面對面按正常考試，按《預防及控制疾病(禁止羣組聚集)規例 》，為違法行為。可以打1823，而且如繼續考試，其成績也可以司法覆核，以非法考試為由要求撤銷。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T15:25:02.000Z","msg":"第一句啱呀<br />\n<br />\n但係第二句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n司法覆核大學成績係可行 但係你揾理據會有好大困難<br />\n<br />\nbetween 強烈反對<br />\n淨間其他學系有樣學樣 咪會加大傳播風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n意大利直情話唔使考<br />\n香港延期咪得囉！"},{"pid":"469882b949534d1d29392fe82a9d66b9cc0fd96a","tid":1949310,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T15:40:43.000Z","msg":"直程醫科生今年上前線者可以免試畢業啦"},{"pid":"